Class DataList

java.lang.Object
  de.must.appletserver.RemoteElement
      de.must.appletserver.DataList
All Implemented Interfaces:
AppletTalker, Remotable, RemoteContent, Storable, DataChangeListener
public class DataList
extends RemoteElement
implements Storable, DataChangeListener

Component to sub-select sub-items of an entity. Registered data components will be reloaded, when the selection changes.
